{"tid":2232180,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"紅外相機偷拍發現，野兔開始吃肉了！","createTime":"2020-10-06T08:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:28:58.000Z","uid":3747,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"73cec767bb07d873019d37ae141c36dba6f494f5","tid":2232180,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"逼急了，兔子也會咬人！這句話恐怕很多人都聽說過，意思是說，兔子是草食動物，不會對肉類動物下口，但如果你把它逼急了，要它的命，它也很可能會咬你一口！<br />\n<br />\n但是現在，恐怕已經不只是兔子咬人的問題了，兔子甚至有可能會吃人。阿爾伯塔大學博士研究生佩爾斯專門研究氣候變化如何影響雪鞋兔&mdash;&mdash;北美洲一種常見野兔的生活，從2015年1月開始，佩爾斯和他的同事們在加拿大育空地區克盧恩湖區，觀察到大量雪鞋兔食用動物屍體的現象，甚至它們的天敵也未能倖免，自然秩序似乎已轟然坍塌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://changepw.com/?p=122497&amp;fbclid=IwAR1P8f556TiTkPgYiWVRIn4foB_A87zpBpGGrzR7AKdUogvKVSV8QIz7Dpw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchangepw.com%2F%3Fp%3D122497%26fbclid%3DIwAR1P8f556TiTkPgYiWVRIn4foB_A87zpBpGGrzR7AKdUogvKVSV8QIz7Dpw&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKAZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=021c9e58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://changepw.com/?p=122497&amp;fbclid=IwAR1P8f556TiTkPgYiWVRIn4foB_A87zpBpGGrzR7AKdUogvKVSV8QIz7Dpw</a>"},{"pid":"255689bcccd29161dcec6b2a9377f30afc6d6caf","tid":2232180,"uid":225148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:18:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id917932200?pt=39040802&amp;ct=Media1GIFV2&amp;mt=8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fapp%2Fapple-store%2Fid917932200%3Fpt%3D39040802%26ct%3DMedia1GIFV2%26mt%3D8&h=6664af52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ed82a077f1665f7d344b112e5219d750caf5ff4","tid":2232180,"uid":110832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:19:20.000Z","msg":"兔係邪惡象徵"},{"pid":"c8d41644d252abb8e56ff6f10dcc4655a532febb","tid":2232180,"uid":225148,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"255689bcccd29161dcec6b2a9377f30afc6d6caf","tid":2232180,"uid":225148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202